# Understand custom Response Types - app.studyraid.com
created: 2025-01-26, last updated: 2025-09-19, [Read more](https://app.studyraid.com/en/read/12490/403884/custom-response-types)

Hapi.js enables
**custom response types** through the
`response` object, allowing tailored data formats (JSON, XML, HTML) based on client needs.
